Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:18.27,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}若要唤出情感之名 则无休无止无穷无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:26.36,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}你的眼神传来呼唤 我以本能即可分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:28.20,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}相伴相随
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:29.45,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}不离不弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:33.03,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}无论光明抑或黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:36.91,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}如紧凑相连的拼图零片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:41.17,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}一切皆有其因果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.58,0:22:45.42,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}萍水相逢也好 命中注定也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:50.09,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}终将指引我们走向所坚信的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:56.85,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}赤诚真心 逐步升温
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.85,0:23:00.69,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}无虚情假意 非利益所趋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:05.44,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}以真实自我
